/* Neodisk — base (English) localization.
   Keys are the English source strings exactly as they appear in SwiftUI
   Text/Button/Label/… literals (SwiftUI uses the literal itself as the lookup
   key) plus the strings passed through NSLocalizedString / LocalizedStringKey
   in code. Interpolations compile to %@ (all counts go through .formatted(),
   so they are strings) or %lld. Translations may reorder with %1$@, %2$@, … */

